Obfuscated
==============

Obfuscated allows you to obfuscate the primary keys of your ActiveRecord models
which use autoincrementing integer ids.


Example
=======

@user = User.first
@user.hashed_id
# "9b46a2e8c9db"
@same_user = User.find_by_hashed_id( "9b46a2e8c9db" )


